data.description: Back on the Market! Tucked away in the the desirable Prestwick Glen Addition! Right next to the Golf Course! 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath Amazing Home w/Master BDRM Suite & half bath on Main! Almost 1800 Square Ft, this home offers new flooring throughout with an open floorplan, sun filled entry, loft walkway overlooking the large great room with vaulted ceilings, fireplace and windows on each side for added natural lighting. Spacious Kitchen w/all Appliances Staying! Formal dining room, breakfast nook and a Huge Pantry. 2 bedrooms Upstairs w/a Utility Room for additional Storage. Porches w/Access from your Master Suite & Great room to Relax Outside in Your Own Private Backyard Sanctuary with a fully fenced yard. New HVAC system aswell. Home Buyers Warranty Included!
